refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public boolMysqlndUhConnection::restartPSession mysqlnd_connectionconnection
Redémarre une connexion mysqlnd persistante.

&reftitle.parameters;


  connection



    Gestionnaire de connexion Mysqlnd. Ne pas modifier !

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 Retourne &true; en cas de succès.
 Sinon, retourne &false;

  &reftitle.examples;



    Exemple avec MysqlndUhConnection::restartPSession


<?php
class proxy extends MysqlndUhConnection {
 public function ping($res) {
  printf("%s(%s)\n", __METHOD__, var_export(func_get_args(), true));
  $ret = parent::ping($res);
  printf("%s retourne %s\n", __METHOD__, var_export($ret, true));
  return $ret;
 }
}
mysqlnd_uh_set_connection_proxy(new proxy());

$mysqli = new mysqli("localhost", "root", "", "test");
$mysqli->ping();
?>


    &example.outputs;


proxy::restartPSession(array (
  0 => NULL,
))
proxy::restartPSession retourne true
